test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 6] == [6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 6
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 12
  Full diff:
  - [6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
  + [2, 4, 6]
test_large_range:
assert [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7] == [3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 3
  Left contains one more item: 7
  Full diff:
  - [3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  + [2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  ?  +++
